<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>This Privacy Policy explains how FinPlan collects and uses information when you use the site.</p>

<h3>Cookies</h3>
<p>We use cookies and similar technologies to improve our calculators and analyze traffic. Cookies are small files stored on your device to improve
site functionality. You can disable cookies in your browser, though some features may not function correctly.</p>

<h3>Personalized ads & third-party services</h3>
<p>Third parties (e.g., advertising partners) may use cookies to serve personalized ads based on your visits to this and other sites. You can opt out of personalized ads in your browser or via the ad partner’s settings.
We may also use third-party analytics and advertising providers. These providers may set cookies and collect information about your use of the site. We do not sell personal information. Consult the third-party providers for details on their data practices.</p>

<h3>Data we collect</h3>
<p>We collect aggregated and non-identifying information to help improve the site and calculators, including:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Pages viewed and interactions with our calculators (aggregated)</li>
    <li>Device and browser information</li>
    <li>Approximate location derived from IP address</li>
</ul>
<p>We do not sell personal information.</p>

<p>If you have concerns about privacy, contact us via the Contact page or at <a href="mailto:privacy@rewealthen.com">privacy@rewealthen.com</a>.</p>

